<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .code-container {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .code {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: #00838f;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #eeeeee;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{app_name}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>{{text1}}</p>
        <p>{{text2}} <strong>{{app_name}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>{{text3}}</p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center;">Veya aşağıdaki aktivasyon kodunu kullanabilirsiniz:</p>
        
        <div class="code-container">
            <div class="code">{{hash}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <p style="text-align: center;">Bu e-posta otomatik olarak gönderilmiştir, lütfen yanıtlamayınız.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{app_name}} - Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>